        "created_at": "2021-07-11T20:19:30.000Z",
        "cooked": "<p>Thanks for the note Sean.  I picked this up from Winex a few months ago but they would only ship to my CA locker.  I usually wait for cooler temps to ship to me here in HI.  What\u2019s your sense on age ability for this wine?</p>",
